                                <p class="product__option__name">
                                  <span class="option__item">차콜그레이</span>
                                  <span class="option__item">68 XL</span>
                                  <span class="option__item">1개</span>
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="review-container">
                        <div class="review-util">
                          <div class="benefit">
                            <p class="mileage"><strong>1,500 M</strong> 적립 예정</p>
                            <p class="badge">Micro Influencer BADGE</p>
                          </div>
                          <div class="util">
                            <button type="button" class="button">수정</button>
                            <button type="button" class="button">삭제</button>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="review">
                          <div class="review__info">
                            <div class="rating">
                              <span class="point__icon">
                                <!-- 별점: width: 100%: 별5개, width: 20%: 별 1개 -->
                                <span class="point__value" style="width: 80%"></span>
                              </span>
                              <span class="point__number">4</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="date">
                              2021.03.18
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="review__content">
                            오랜만에 마음에 드는 쇼핑 했어요~ 미리 다른 제품 살 때 구입했는데 요즘 날씨로 봐서는 4월부터 잘 입을 것 같아요
